      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For clothing, a charcoal or navy suit with a crisp white shirt and a silk tie is the universal baseline for men, while a well-tailored, dark pant suit with a silk blouse is appropriate for women. Behaviorally, practice active listening—maintain steady eye contact while nodding thoughtfully, which signals engagement without being aggressive. At a business dinner, wait for the host to initiate toasts and always keep your hands visible on the table, never resting them in your lap.",
      "source": "target",
